title: Zed ult with kled q bug
body:
Kled's q can knock zed out of his ult. Pretty annoying, happened twice
e.g kled q's zed, zed uses ult then kled's q pull activates and pulls zed out of ult.

replies.body:
Hey there,

I'm not sure if this is intended or not as I haven't yet gotten to play kled.

You might still want to post a thread over on the [Report a Bug (NA)](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) board just incase, before posting please be sure to read the "[How to Report a Game Bug](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report/3mQGBEjA-how-to-report-a-game-bug)" sticky thread.
